This software uses an external library for string formatting. (format.cc format.h)

Example call for this program:
mpirun -np 1 ./heat 10 10 100 0.0000001 100 0.01 0.01 0.5 2

Parameters are
-grid points in x direction
-grid points in y direction
-number of cg iterations
-eps for cg (stopping condition)
-time steps to calculate
-alpha
-kappa
-method (1: implicit; 0.5 Crank-Nicholson; 0: explicit) Values inbetween are also possible
-output interval for vtk

Make file can be generated by using cmake. Specifiy "export CXX=mpic++" before your first cmake configure!
